file_content.text: You've only made matters worse for yourself.
Duly noted.
Uh huh. [Hang up]
I wasn't looking for a fight.
I doubt a jury would agree.
Try anything like this again and I'll be paying you a visit.
Don't mess with me, Jedi.
Justice will be done. I promise you.
This mean big-traders not want to put boss face on things anymore?
We've got nothing left to discuss with Adascorp.
It's time we left.
That too bad. Blizz wanted to ask to put Blizz face on things too.
It was all a trick to spring this ambush.
Afraid so.
Aww... Blizz wanted to buy thing with boss face for keepsake.
What do you think, idiot?
Blizz not clueless....
What that noise?
Security finally figured out things didn't go to plan.
An alert.
It means trouble's coming. Let's move.
Get ready for a fight.
Just follow me and shoot anyone who gets in our way.
Don't worry about it.
Think there's a safe in here?
I'm not sticking around to find out.
Don't care.
Planning to bill them later?
Never miss a beat, do you?
Are you serious?
Hate to leave empty-handed.
Okay, I can take a hint. After you.
I'll search the bodies; you check the room.
Good idea.
Gotcha.
Figures. What's the plan?
Keep searching. I'll hold them off.
The plan's the same.
Take your time. I've got this covered.
Security won't be a problem.
Now this brings back some memories.
Whatever's here probably ain't worth fighting over.
Let's just go.
Teach them to mess with Mandos.
Kellian Jarro. You took down "the Mandalorian Killer"?
He was my final target in the Great Hunt.
I did.
Good target.
You seem surprised.
Don't believe it?
A little.
Blasted him and the ship he flew in on.
Among other things.
Wish I'd seen that.
More trouble.
Just an inconvenience.
We're leaving anyway.
Unless Adascorp's fielding giant walkers, I think we'll be fine.
That's stretching it.
I thought the body count was low anyway.
More fun.
I can't believe this was all a setup!
We'll have to be more selective with future job offers.
Can't be so trusting anymore.
That'll be tough. The SIS doesn't need to fake documents--they make real ones. We'll have to trust your gut.
I was just getting used to the idea of being a household name.
It's really too bad.
Well, who wants to be on stimpacks anyway? You're already famous where it counts, right?
You said this was legit. What do I pay you for?
Check your sources next time.
Sorry I didn't spot the legitimate authentication provided by the largest intelligence network in the galaxy.
You want predictions like that, go rub a Jedi on the head.
Uh-oh, looks like Adascorp security's going on full alert.
Let's go before they make any more offers.
Time for our exit.
I'm way above their pay grade.
They won't pose a problem.
Just what I need to relieve some pent-up frustration.
Good, I'm in a killing mood.
